item.description: Kristina studies the importance of size in ecological systems and how it responds to changes in the environment.

item.title: Apoorva Pandey
item.description: Apoorva is an Undergraduate Student in Computer Science. He has been selected in Google Summer of Code 2018 to work with us. He will be working on the project Status Server and Dashboard that will be used for checking the availability and installation of datasets available through Data Retriever.
